    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >你，快来成为本喵的开罐器吧喵！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >请在猫咪任务中解开各种谜题，拯救被困在外星次元的猫咪们吧！被救出的猫咪会前往猫叔之家，并与猫叔一起创造美好记忆。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >现在就去拯救可爱的猫咪们吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139640/extras/ac10e4089ee762aee1909bbfa746b515.poster.avif?t=1739331531\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139640/extras/ac10e4089ee762aee1909bbfa746b515.webm?t=1739331531\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139640/extras/ac10e4089ee762aee1909bbfa746b515.mp4?t=1739331531\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >丰富多彩的谜题</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索推箱子谜题，寻找猫咪吧！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >基于经典的推箱子玩法，在各次元设置了一系列新颖的变体谜题。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一关都精心设计了独特的挑战，点燃您的思维火花。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139640/extras/f4daee709d83b181baabb633ef1f8656.poster.avif?t=1739331531\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139640/extras/f4daee709d83b181baabb633ef1f8656.webm?t=1739331531\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139640/extras/f4daee709d83b181baabb633ef1f8656.mp4?t=1739331531\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >建设家园</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >被救出的猫咪会在猫叔之家安枕无忧地生活，并与猫叔度过美好时光。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可在猫叔之家与猫咪们一起玩耍。不过猫咪们可能颇为挑剔，请温柔谨慎地接近它们！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >请利用在不同次元发现的石板装饰猫叔之家，发掘猫叔的不同魅力。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139640/extras/7a8cd64f0d1279054748a524cfcb50a9.poster.avif?t=1739331531\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139640/extras/7a8cd64f0d1279054748a524cfcb50a9.webm?t=1739331531\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139640/extras/7a8cd64f0d1279054748a524cfcb50a9.mp4?t=1739331531\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >搜集猫咪</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >请聚集性格迥异的猫咪朋友们！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与救出的猫咪一起相处，积累好感，就能收获特别的互动与惊喜。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139640/extras/eacc039e1c203f800a053a30d9111df8.poster.avif?t=1739331531\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139640/extras/eacc039e1c203f800a053a30d9111df8.webm?t=1739331531\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139640/extras/eacc039e1c203f800a053a30d9111df8.mp4?t=1739331531\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >超越次元的奇妙故事</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与猫咪变得亲密，即可解锁更多隐藏故事。猫咪们丰富多彩的故事会以漫画的形式生动呈现。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >请多和猫咪们互动交流，尽情领略缤纷多彩的故事所带来的魅力。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139640/extras/6f188480f0ccb6a2b439b1a7ee25a9eb.poster.avif?t=1739331531\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139640/extras/6f188480f0ccb6a2b439b1a7ee25a9eb.webm?t=1739331531\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139640/extras/6f188480f0ccb6a2b439b1a7ee25a9eb.mp4?t=1739331531\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >现在就去拯救可爱的猫咪们吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
